<div class="com-share" data-id="23955" data-title="《李嘉诚的百佳超市，在大本营广州也不行了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23955/medium/23955.jpg?1458101755" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23955.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
